  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK580">
<l>peyakkaṇṭu nañcuṇ ṭamaivar nayattakka </l>
<l> nākarikam vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who desire (to cultivate that degree of) urbanity which all shall love, even after swallowing the poison served to them by their friends, will be friendly with them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
